Hit him!

520
00:33:16,014 --> 00:33:17,210
Hit him!

521
00:33:17,290 --> 00:33:18,732
Hit him, smash him.

522
00:33:20,575 --> 00:33:22,745
Hit him!

523
00:33:23,250 --> 00:33:24,650
Here sister, adorn him.

524
00:33:24,887 --> 00:33:27,782
O wow, this is absolutely
an original garland.

525
00:33:28,153 --> 00:33:29,216
I'll be right back.

526
00:33:29,997 --> 00:33:32,316
Move! Move! Move! Move!

527
00:33:36,530 --> 00:33:37,919
Get up! Get up!

528
00:33:37,999 --> 00:33:41,023
Forgive me!

529
00:33:41,480 --> 00:33:44,118
If you ever come to
this village again.

530
00:33:44,151 --> 00:33:47,311
Then I will beat you to a pulp.

531
00:33:47,391 --> 00:33:49,276
What?
- Beat me to a pulp.

532
00:33:49,356 --> 00:33:50,471
Yes! Run!

533
00:33:50,863 --> 00:33:52,341
Run!

534
00:33:57,022 --> 00:34:00,631
Great Shalu, you taught
that goon a nice lesson.

535
00:34:00,871 --> 00:34:02,363
Look at how he ran.

536
00:34:02,443 --> 00:34:04,161
He must have learned his lesson!

537
00:34:04,288 --> 00:34:05,335
He would bother us everyday.

538
00:34:05,447 --> 00:34:09,303
Now he will never come
to this village again.

539
00:34:09,558 --> 00:34:11,224
Live peacefully.

540
00:34:11,431 --> 00:34:13,399
May God bless you!

541
00:34:16,174 --> 00:34:18,055
Shalu, you were really great.

542
00:34:18,142 --> 00:34:21,440
You taught a nice lesson
to that strong goon.

543
00:34:21,529 --> 00:34:24,351
Mister, this was a
very small example.

544
00:34:24,567 --> 00:34:25,951
Whoever has locked
horns with Shalu..

545
00:34:26,031 --> 00:34:28,031
..she has always taught
him a lesson like this.

546
00:34:28,111 --> 00:34:30,831
Oh yes, did you get a room
in the guest house?

547
00:34:30,995 --> 00:34:31,831
Yes I did.

548
00:34:31,911 --> 00:34:34,191
Bye then.

549
00:34:39,445 --> 00:34:41,471
Suraj has crossed all limits.

550
00:34:41,694 --> 00:34:43,396
He has been missing from
home since yesterday.

551
00:34:43,476 --> 00:34:44,661
Without informing!

552
00:34:44,741 --> 00:34:45,729
Do you know anything?

553
00:34:45,843 --> 00:34:48,822
No.. maybe he went with
his friends for a picnic.

554
00:34:48,902 --> 00:34:50,231
With whose permission?

555
00:34:50,657 --> 00:34:52,823
Only your permission is
followed in this house.

556
00:34:52,903 --> 00:34:54,524
But if you..
- Keep quiet, please!

557
00:34:54,604 --> 00:34:55,991
Secretary.
- Yes madam.

558
00:34:56,245 --> 00:34:57,685
What are you looking at?

559
00:34:57,765 --> 00:34:59,006
Quickly take the car out and go!

560
00:34:59,086 --> 00:34:59,649
I understood!

561
00:34:59,729 --> 00:35:01,562
Go and search for Suraj sir,
and bring him before you..

562
00:35:01,642 --> 00:35:02,363
..either dead or alive.

563
00:35:02,443 --> 00:35:03,242
Shut up!

564
00:35:03,373 --> 00:35:05,805
Understand the situation
before speaking!

565
00:35:05,885 --> 00:35:07,405
Go and search for him, shut up.

566
00:35:07,485 --> 00:35:09,085
Yes madam! Sorry.

567
00:35:10,749 --> 00:35:11,794
Shall I keep seated
or shall I get up?

568
00:35:11,946 --> 00:35:13,725
Keep seated!
- Thank you!

569
00:35:15,165 --> 00:35:17,925
This boy has really troubled me.

570
00:35:18,525 --> 00:35:19,965
If Suraj is not found by evening..

571
00:35:20,045 --> 00:35:23,645
..then what will I tell
Mrs. Poonawala.

572
00:35:23,725 --> 00:35:27,205
Mrs. Chunawala..
- Mrs. Poonawala, not Chunawala.

573
00:35:27,285 --> 00:35:28,485
Yes, slip of tongue.

574
00:35:28,673 --> 00:35:32,805
I will explain to Mrs. Chunawala..
no, Mrs. Poonawala nicely.

575
00:35:32,885 --> 00:35:34,365
Mr. Bhandari!

576
00:35:34,717 --> 00:35:37,825
Don't try to be too
free with my friends!

577
00:35:37,905 --> 00:35:39,005
You know my nature.

578
00:35:39,077 --> 00:35:41,298
What else do I know in this
world other than your nature?

579
00:35:41,552 --> 00:35:44,456
Then listen one thing carefully.
- Yes.

580
00:35:44,528 --> 00:35:48,327
My son should be here
within 24 hours!

581
00:35:48,809 --> 00:35:51,307
Look that depends on the Lord.

582
00:35:51,435 --> 00:35:53,942
But as far as 24 hours are
concerned, that's impossible.

583
00:35:54,101 --> 00:35:55,673
You need at least 9 months for that.

584
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:59,269
Mr. Bhandari! - Slowly, or oil
will sprout out from earth.

585
00:35:59,433 --> 00:36:00,999
My head is about to explode!

586
00:36:03,502 --> 00:36:05,153
Do you need an atom bomb?

587
00:36:05,233 --> 00:36:05,708
No, isn't it?

588
00:36:05,820 --> 00:36:07,693
She is enough to blast
the entire world.

589
00:36:08,533 --> 00:36:10,128
Think what my condition is.

590
00:36:10,270 --> 00:36:10,893
Greetings sir.
- Greetings.

591
00:36:10,973 --> 00:36:12,213
I have brought tea for you.

592
00:36:12,293 --> 00:36:13,693
Bring it, I need tea.

593
00:36:13,773 --> 00:36:17,853
Tell me sir, did you face any
difficulty in the night?

594
00:36:18,133 --> 00:36:19,813
And did you sleep peacefully?

595
00:36:20,464 --> 00:36:21,213
I slept very peacefully.

596
00:36:21,694 --> 00:36:25,333
Really sir!
- And I saw very nice dreams.

597
00:36:25,466 --> 00:36:26,413
Dreams!

598
00:36:28,494 --> 00:36:31,213
Watchman! The first thing that I
sighted entering this village..

599
00:36:31,293 --> 00:36:35,394
..her name is Shalu.

600
00:36:37,522 --> 00:36:38,453
What a beautiful face!

601
00:36:39,700 --> 00:36:41,013
What melodious voice!

602
00:36:41,773 --> 00:36:43,533
She talks nicely too!

603
00:36:43,933 --> 00:36:45,773
And she is so brave!

604
00:36:46,333 --> 00:36:52,573
Sir, it is so great if 1 girl has
so many qualities. - Isn't it?

605
00:36:52,943 --> 00:36:56,613
And watchman, I have been dreaming
about her the entire night.

606
00:36:56,786 --> 00:36:57,453
Really!

607
00:36:57,533 --> 00:36:59,373
That's why you are looking so happy.

608
00:36:59,453 --> 00:37:01,853
Sir, where does that girl live?

609
00:37:02,303 --> 00:37:03,213
Even I don't know that!

610
00:37:03,293 --> 00:37:05,613
I was thinking about asking you.

611
00:37:05,693 --> 00:37:08,293
What does her parents do,
where does she live?

612
00:37:08,507 --> 00:37:10,733
Sir, I will find that out.
- Yes!

613
00:37:10,813 --> 00:37:12,780
Sir! Sir!

614
00:37:12,860 --> 00:37:14,173
Hide me somewhere, sir!

615
00:37:14,343 --> 00:37:15,587
Hide me somewhere!

616
00:37:15,835 --> 00:37:16,654
What is the matter, Shalu?

617
00:37:16,734 --> 00:37:17,557
Why are you so scared?

618
00:37:17,637 --> 00:37:19,773
What shall I tell you,
this is what you say..

619
00:37:19,853 --> 00:37:22,133
..l didn't do anything
and fell into trouble.

620
00:37:22,420 --> 00:37:24,457
Yesterday I had thrashed that goon.
- Yes.

621
00:37:24,537 --> 00:37:27,213
Today he has come with his goons.

622
00:37:27,293 --> 00:37:28,533
And Shalu is in trouble.

623
00:37:28,690 --> 00:37:30,093
He might come here too.

624
00:37:30,173 --> 00:37:31,381
Hide me somewhere!

625
00:37:31,461 --> 00:37:32,293
Why are you worried, I am there!

626
00:37:32,373 --> 00:37:34,573
I will take care of everything.
- Yes.

627
00:37:34,909 --> 00:37:37,213
You will take care of everything!
- Yes, of course I will.

628
00:37:37,293 --> 00:37:39,853
Mister, then may your children
have a long life.

629
00:37:40,773 --> 00:37:43,933
For your information I must tell
you, I don't have children!

630
00:37:44,493 --> 00:37:46,853
Why, you couldn't have them.

631
00:37:47,152 --> 00:37:47,893
Of course I would have.

632
00:37:48,255 --> 00:37:50,093
If I would have been married.

633
00:37:51,429 --> 00:37:52,973
You are not married.

634
00:37:53,724 --> 00:37:54,973
I am unmarried too.

635
00:37:55,413 --> 00:37:56,693
You are not married!

636
00:37:57,475 --> 00:37:59,533
Then I am happier to meet you!

637
00:37:59,792 --> 00:38:00,573
Yes!

638
00:38:00,813 --> 00:38:02,630
Watchman, Shalu has come.

639
00:38:02,710 --> 00:38:03,733
Go bring tea for her!

640
00:38:03,813 --> 00:38:05,293
I will just bring it sir.
-Please come.

641
00:38:07,316 --> 00:38:08,551
Why are you turning back,
no one will come.

642
00:38:08,631 --> 00:38:09,813
Come, come.

643
00:38:11,541 --> 00:38:13,613
Sit on the sofa, not down there.

644
00:38:13,813 --> 00:38:15,653
Here.
- Then, what is this sofa for.

645
00:38:16,084 --> 00:38:18,333
Sit, sit.

646
00:38:21,093 --> 00:38:23,173
Shall I tell you one thing, mister?
- Yes.

647
00:38:24,333 --> 00:38:27,773
You have so much respect
for the poor.

648
00:38:28,198 --> 00:38:30,213
This difference between
rich and the poor.

649
00:38:30,354 --> 00:38:32,173
We humans have made it.

650
00:38:32,497 --> 00:38:34,333
For the Lord, all human
beings are the same.

651
00:38:34,956 --> 00:38:35,853
They are, isn't it?

652
00:38:36,293 --> 00:38:37,973
Shall I tell you one
more thing, sir? - Yes tell me.

653
00:38:38,533 --> 00:38:40,613
I don't understand what you say.

654
00:38:40,693 --> 00:38:41,973
But it feels very nice to hear.

655
00:38:43,741 --> 00:38:46,973
Shalu, shall I ask you something?
- Ask.

656
00:38:47,757 --> 00:38:50,013
Where is your house?
- Very close-by.

657
00:38:50,093 --> 00:38:51,373
You can come now if you want.

658
00:38:51,552 --> 00:38:54,653
I will give you corn bread and
leafy vegetable curry to eat.

659
00:38:54,813 --> 00:38:56,373
We will eat that later.

660
00:38:56,453 --> 00:38:58,253
Shall we first take a
look at your village?

661
00:38:58,333 --> 00:39:00,744
Village! Come on.
- Come on.

662
00:39:05,425 --> 00:39:07,573
Wrapped in the arms
of the mountains..

663
00:39:07,653 --> 00:39:09,813
..your Lakhanpur really
is very beautiful, Shalu.

664
00:39:10,573 --> 00:39:12,133
I feel like staying back here.

665
00:39:12,853 --> 00:39:14,613
There is such serenity here.

666
00:39:15,181 --> 00:39:18,293
That means you liked
my village very much.

667
00:39:18,453 --> 00:39:19,493
Very nice.

668
00:39:19,945 --> 00:39:21,133
But not as nice as you.

669
00:39:22,039 --> 00:39:23,493
Why are you joking mister.

670
00:39:23,784 --> 00:39:25,213
What is so special about Shalu?

671
00:39:25,493 --> 00:39:27,093
You won't understand Shalu.

672
00:39:27,173 --> 00:39:28,618
By seeing some faces
you understand..

673
00:39:28,698 --> 00:39:30,893
..the Lord has taken a lot of
effort in their creation.

674
00:39:31,815 --> 00:39:36,373
And seeing your face, I feel
framing it in my eyes.

675
00:39:36,693 --> 00:39:38,053
Don't move! Don't move! Yes.

676
00:39:39,817 --> 00:39:40,773
You move a lot.

677
00:39:40,853 --> 00:39:42,133
If you move the photograph
will not be nice.

678
00:39:42,213 --> 00:39:43,373
Smile.

679
00:39:44,520 --> 00:39:45,173
Are you ready now?

680
00:39:45,494 --> 00:39:46,213
What?

681
00:39:46,293 --> 00:39:47,373
What are you saying, mister?

682
00:39:47,771 --> 00:39:50,453
It means, are you ready or not.

683
00:39:50,906 --> 00:39:52,053
I am ready.

684
00:39:52,133 --> 00:39:52,933
Yes, very good.

685
00:39:53,053 --> 00:39:54,373
Don't move.

686
00:39:56,735 --> 00:39:58,133
Done.
- First class.

687
00:39:58,573 --> 00:39:59,373
Come on.

688
00:40:00,145 --> 00:40:03,813
Except for an uncle, I don't
have anyone else mister.

689
00:40:04,014 --> 00:40:04,573
Really.

690
00:40:04,653 --> 00:40:06,533
He is my mother and my father.

691
00:40:07,093 --> 00:40:08,938
He loves me so much.

692
00:40:09,018 --> 00:40:12,293
I feel like taking care
of him all my life.

693
00:40:12,849 --> 00:40:14,213
All your life!

694
00:40:15,333 --> 00:40:18,893
That's fine Shalu, but you will
have to leave him someday.

695
00:40:18,973 --> 00:40:20,293
Why?

696
00:40:20,636 --> 00:40:23,133
Don't you want to get married?

697
00:40:25,093 --> 00:40:28,653
Who knows mister, whether
I will get married or not?

698
00:40:28,851 --> 00:40:30,333
You will, why you won't get married!

699
00:40:30,854 --> 00:40:33,093
It is said, matches
are made in heaven.

700
00:40:34,087 --> 00:40:36,573
There must be someone
in your fate too.

701
00:40:36,894 --> 00:40:39,093
On that note I remembered..

702
00:40:39,434 --> 00:40:41,413
..an astrologer told
me the same thing.

703
00:40:41,715 --> 00:40:45,053
That your fate lies on your palms.

704
00:40:45,645 --> 00:40:48,131
Mister, do you know
how to read palms?

705
00:40:48,211 --> 00:40:49,564
Read palms.
- Yes.

706
00:40:49,644 --> 00:40:50,813
Read your palm.
- Yes.

707
00:40:51,333 --> 00:40:52,413
Yes, I can.

708
00:40:52,493 --> 00:40:54,253
Read my palm.

709
00:40:54,333 --> 00:40:56,173
Shall I see your palm?
- Yes. - Sit.

710
00:41:02,213 --> 00:41:05,573
Mister, you have been holding
my hand for so long.

711
00:41:06,199 --> 00:41:08,616
What's written in my hands,
what do the lines say..

712
00:41:08,696 --> 00:41:09,613
..tell me something.

713
00:41:09,693 --> 00:41:11,333
In your palms.

714
00:41:12,093 --> 00:41:13,773
It is written Shalu..

715
00:41:15,748 --> 00:41:17,413
Shalu your hands are very beautiful.

716
00:41:18,653 --> 00:41:20,791
You have already said that.

717
00:41:20,871 --> 00:41:22,133
Let go of my hand.

718
00:41:23,723 --> 00:41:27,613
Mister. This Lord Shiva
temple is very famous.

719
00:41:27,693 --> 00:41:30,093
There is a Shiva's veneration
held here every year too.

720
00:41:30,173 --> 00:41:31,253
Really.
- Yes.

721
00:41:31,413 --> 00:41:34,293
Whatever you wish for with the
true heart, it is fulfilled.

722
00:41:34,573 --> 00:41:36,715
This temple is so powerful.

723
00:41:48,206 --> 00:41:49,253
Shalu.

724
00:41:51,333 --> 00:41:53,613
Let us wish for something together.

725
00:41:53,813 --> 00:41:56,253
Yes, but tell me what
we should wish for.

726
00:41:59,060 --> 00:42:00,613
Leave my hand, mister.

727
00:42:01,142 --> 00:42:02,493
You want to free this hand.

728
00:42:03,019 --> 00:42:05,013
And I want to ask for
you from Lord Shiva.

729
00:42:06,253 --> 00:42:07,333
This is my desire Shalu.

730
00:42:08,173 --> 00:42:10,653
That we are bonded
in such a relation.

731
00:42:10,864 --> 00:42:12,893
That no one can ever break.

732
00:42:17,053 --> 00:42:20,253
Look mister, I am a simple
girl from the village.

733
00:42:21,213 --> 00:42:24,973
I can't understand what you say.

734
00:42:25,613 --> 00:42:27,973
What are your intentions?

735
00:42:28,533 --> 00:42:29,853
Shall I tell you?

736
00:42:30,133 --> 00:42:31,893
Yes, say it.

737
00:42:33,493 --> 00:42:35,053
Shalu, I have fallen
in love with you.

738
00:42:36,013 --> 00:42:38,573
What? Really mister?

739
00:42:38,735 --> 00:42:39,813
Yes Shalu.

740
00:42:51,693 --> 00:42:52,813
Shalu!

741
00:42:53,082 --> 00:42:54,173
Shameless! Characterless!

742
00:42:54,837 --> 00:42:57,493
Weren't you ashamed defaming me!

743
00:42:57,813 --> 00:42:58,853
Why didn't you die of shame!

744
00:42:59,182 --> 00:43:01,253
But uncle..
- I am no more your uncle!

745
00:43:01,333 --> 00:43:03,335
Listen! You are needlessly
getting angry on her!

746
00:43:03,415 --> 00:43:04,253
It is not her fault!

747
00:43:04,333 --> 00:43:05,933
Keep quiet mister!

748
00:43:06,259 --> 00:43:08,293
I have seen everything
with my own eyes.

749
00:43:08,573 --> 00:43:12,173
You city people always do
this with us village people.

750
00:43:12,253 --> 00:43:13,693
We sow the seeds.

751
00:43:13,773 --> 00:43:15,022
We look after it.

752
00:43:15,226 --> 00:43:18,573
When the harvest is ready..
then you people come to cut it.

753
00:43:18,693 --> 00:43:20,013
Get one thing clear, sir.

754
00:43:20,093 --> 00:43:22,933
She is my child! Jagat Dada's!

755
00:43:23,053 --> 00:43:26,933
I will kill her,
but I will not let anyone touch her!

756
00:43:27,222 --> 00:43:28,939
Come on shameless!
- Uncle.

757
00:43:29,019 --> 00:43:30,280
Come on!

758
00:43:30,360 --> 00:43:32,013
Your uncle is dead!

759
00:43:46,428 --> 00:43:49,063
Mister, you!

760
00:43:49,334 --> 00:43:50,093
Shalu!

761
00:43:51,210 --> 00:43:53,926
Shalu, I am very sorry that..

762
00:43:54,006 --> 00:43:55,417
Why mister!

763
00:43:56,321 --> 00:43:59,721
Lovers have to face more sorrows.

764
00:44:00,116 --> 00:44:01,001
No Shalu.

765
00:44:01,467 --> 00:44:03,427
I am responsible for these sorrows.

766
00:44:03,507 --> 00:44:05,107
And it has brought me here.

767
00:44:06,387 --> 00:44:10,587
At least my sorrows
were of some use.

768
00:44:11,840 --> 00:44:13,387
But mister, you..
- Shalu!

769
00:44:14,030 --> 00:44:16,667
Mister, you are so stubborn!

770
00:44:16,937 --> 00:44:18,827
You have come again to meet Shalu.

771
00:44:19,187 --> 00:44:23,667
I ask you, do you rich people
have some respect for us poor?

772
00:44:24,027 --> 00:44:26,667
Uncle, why are you taunting
me of being a rich man!

773
00:44:27,128 --> 00:44:29,067
It is true that I was
born in a rich family.

774
00:44:29,147 --> 00:44:33,187
But being poor is neither
a fault nor a crime!

775
00:44:33,267 --> 00:44:34,747
And actually, I haven't
come to meet Shalu..

776
00:44:34,827 --> 00:44:37,187
..I have come to meet you.
- Why?

777
00:44:38,392 --> 00:44:42,587
Uncle.. I want to marry Shalu.

778
00:45:22,143 --> 00:45:23,827
You are capable and close too.

