01:28:59,075 --> 01:29:04,628
Don't want it! Beloved,
are you upset with me.

1536
01:29:04,854 --> 01:29:05,868
I should be upset with you.

1537
01:29:06,324 --> 01:29:07,628
You switched off the electricity,
Shalu.

1538
01:29:07,999 --> 01:29:08,788
What?

1539
01:29:09,031 --> 01:29:11,468
I mean..
- You mean the fuse!

1540
01:29:11,630 --> 01:29:12,741
Yes, that.

1541
01:29:12,821 --> 01:29:14,868
Why did you raise such a
stir in the house, Shalu.

1542
01:29:15,030 --> 01:29:19,868
Beloved, this house belongs to
me as much as it does to you.

1543
01:29:20,026 --> 01:29:21,616
I am the daughter-in-law
of this house.

1544
01:29:21,908 --> 01:29:25,668
And it is my duty to mend anything
that's wrong in this house.

1545
01:29:25,748 --> 01:29:28,457
Shalu, my mother.. mummy.

1546
01:29:28,777 --> 01:29:31,938
Nothing happens in this house
without her permission!

1547
01:29:32,228 --> 01:29:33,749
Why are you locking horns with her?

1548
01:29:33,997 --> 01:29:35,948
Why are you worried?

1549
01:29:36,765 --> 01:29:38,788
It is between me and
my mother-in-law.

1550
01:29:39,228 --> 01:29:40,927
I will deal with her myself.

1551
01:29:42,185 --> 01:29:43,593
Here, drink the milk.

1552
01:29:48,853 --> 01:29:53,228
"What can I do my joys turned
into sorrows.."

1553
01:29:53,423 --> 01:29:57,468
"What can I do my joys turned
into sorrows.."

1554
01:29:57,838 --> 01:30:01,268
"What can I do my joys turned
into sorrows.."

1555
01:30:01,425 --> 01:30:02,468
Father-in-law.

1556
01:30:02,958 --> 01:30:03,788
Father-in-law!

1557
01:30:03,976 --> 01:30:05,211
"What can I do my joys.."

1558
01:30:05,291 --> 01:30:06,308
Come dear, sit.

1559
01:30:06,633 --> 01:30:10,596
I haven't come here to sit, but
to give you your medicine.

1560
01:30:10,844 --> 01:30:11,708
Medicine!

1561
01:30:11,788 --> 01:30:13,357
Why, what's wrong with me?

1562
01:30:13,437 --> 01:30:16,748
You.. you are suffering
from pressure cooker.

1563
01:30:17,132 --> 01:30:18,628
Pressure cooker.
- Yes! - Me!

1564
01:30:19,072 --> 01:30:20,360
Speak softly, or else the
police will arrest you.

1565
01:30:20,440 --> 01:30:22,108
Can any man have pressure cooker!
- No.

1566
01:30:22,918 --> 01:30:23,948
What is it called in Hindi?

1567
01:30:24,391 --> 01:30:26,988
Yes, you have blood pressure.

1568
01:30:27,734 --> 01:30:28,788
Blood pressure!

1569
01:30:30,134 --> 01:30:32,548
What is there to laugh?

1570
01:30:33,166 --> 01:30:34,228
Father-in-law!

1571
01:30:34,787 --> 01:30:37,348
You should take this medicine
every morning, right?

1572
01:30:38,679 --> 01:30:39,708
Right!

1573
01:30:39,994 --> 01:30:41,308
Then why don't you take it.

1574
01:30:42,115 --> 01:30:44,028
Come on, take it.
- Not now dear.

1575
01:30:44,108 --> 01:30:45,261
I will take it later.

1576
01:30:45,341 --> 01:30:46,548
You go, I will take it later.
- You will have to take it.

1577
01:30:46,771 --> 01:30:47,868
Right now.

1578
01:30:53,820 --> 01:30:54,788
Happy.

1579
01:30:55,548 --> 01:30:59,938
If you don't take your medicine
regularly from now on.

1580
01:31:00,311 --> 01:31:01,468
Then I will be very angry.

1581
01:31:01,548 --> 01:31:02,628
No dear.

1582
01:31:03,004 --> 01:31:04,948
Let the entire world be angry
with me, but not you.

1583
01:31:05,964 --> 01:31:08,051
But dear, tell me one thing.

1584
01:31:09,013 --> 01:31:10,388
Who told you that I
have blood pressure?

1585
01:31:10,723 --> 01:31:13,268
Who will tell me?

1586
01:31:13,448 --> 01:31:15,068
I live in this house father-in-law!

1587
01:31:15,443 --> 01:31:19,184
It is my duty to look
after this house.

1588
01:31:19,734 --> 01:31:22,788
And father-in-law, there
is one more thing.

1589
01:31:23,389 --> 01:31:24,388
Tell me dear.

1590
01:31:25,447 --> 01:31:27,713
Whether there is chaos or
destruction in the world.

1591
01:31:28,073 --> 01:31:30,430
Always be happy.

1592
01:31:36,231 --> 01:31:40,263
Dear, I was never happy before.

1593
01:31:41,287 --> 01:31:44,171
But now that you have come,
I will surely be.

1594
01:31:45,337 --> 01:31:46,308
I will.

1595
01:31:47,674 --> 01:31:49,308
At least there is someone in this
house to take care of me.

1596
01:31:50,230 --> 01:31:51,548
Go dear, go.

1597
01:31:53,973 --> 01:31:55,524
Good afternoon Mrs. Bhandari.

1598
01:31:57,806 --> 01:32:00,339
What a pleasant surprise,
chairman sir!

1599
01:32:00,548 --> 01:32:03,228
No phone, no cable, when
did you arrive brother?

1600
01:32:03,308 --> 01:32:06,308
If I had known, I would've come
to the airport to receive you.

1601
01:32:07,598 --> 01:32:08,748
Take a seat.

1602
01:32:09,108 --> 01:32:10,068
No, no.

1603
01:32:10,183 --> 01:32:12,628
I don't have any right
to sit on that chair.

1604
01:32:12,786 --> 01:32:15,548
Because that chair belongs
to the managing director.

1605
01:32:15,628 --> 01:32:17,188
Okay, okay.
- You sit there.

1606
01:32:17,268 --> 01:32:18,388
And I will sit here.

1607
01:32:18,672 --> 01:32:20,788
You were supposed
to come next month.

1608
01:32:20,868 --> 01:32:22,428
How did you return so soon?

1609
01:32:23,132 --> 01:32:25,458
That was my schedule, but the
chairman of Tokyo's firm..

1610
01:32:25,538 --> 01:32:27,528
..is here these days.

1611
01:32:28,153 --> 01:32:30,628
I have a very important
meeting with him today.

1612
01:32:31,166 --> 01:32:34,179
If that meeting is successful, then
tonight we will leave for Frankfurt.

1613
01:32:34,795 --> 01:32:36,268
Leave these business talks aside.

1614
01:32:36,763 --> 01:32:41,708
Tell me, how is my friend, wife
devotee Mr. Kailash Bhandari.

1615
01:32:42,171 --> 01:32:43,268
Come on brother.

1616
01:32:43,457 --> 01:32:44,866
He is very happy.

1617
01:32:45,065 --> 01:32:46,388
He always thinks about you.

1618
01:32:46,468 --> 01:32:49,200
But you don't get time to come home.

1619
01:32:49,548 --> 01:32:50,868
I will come the next time.
- Promise.

1620
01:32:51,242 --> 01:32:52,308
Promise.

1621
01:32:53,334 --> 01:32:56,108
So madam Bhandari, tell me how
is your company running?

1622
01:32:56,595 --> 01:32:57,788
The company is running fine.

1623
01:32:58,028 --> 01:33:00,388
But I need some money
for a new business.

1624
01:33:00,575 --> 01:33:04,108
Actually, the entire capital of
our company is in rotation.

1625
01:33:04,351 --> 01:33:06,628
I don't know what to do and
how to arrange for the money.

1626
01:33:07,082 --> 01:33:09,011
Mrs. Bhandari this is foul.

1627
01:33:09,697 --> 01:33:11,788
You cannot say that
until I am there.

1628
01:33:12,657 --> 01:33:14,708
Don't forget, I am the chairman
of this company..

1629
01:33:14,788 --> 01:33:16,868
..and the financer too.

1630
01:33:17,025 --> 01:33:18,028
Oh yes.

1631
01:33:18,548 --> 01:33:20,748
Tell me,
how much money do you need.

1632
01:33:21,441 --> 01:33:22,708
Right now I need 10 lakh.

1633
01:33:22,788 --> 01:33:25,188
If I require more,
I will ask you for it.

1634
01:33:25,536 --> 01:33:28,188
O sure, why not.

1635
01:34:09,277 --> 01:34:10,388
Why did you leave the dance?

1636
01:34:11,461 --> 01:34:12,388
I was very tired.

1637
01:34:12,468 --> 01:34:13,788
Then order for something cold,
you will feel fresh!

1638
01:34:13,957 --> 01:34:15,722
Waiter!
- No, let it be.

1639
01:34:16,548 --> 01:34:19,215
Vicky, I had told you
something yesterday.

1640
01:34:21,573 --> 01:34:23,673
I completely forgot about
it because of this disco.

1641
01:34:24,276 --> 01:34:25,868
Here, this sister-in-law 3,000.

1642
01:34:26,769 --> 01:34:27,787
Will this do?

1643
01:34:27,867 --> 01:34:29,028
Of course.

1644
01:34:29,308 --> 01:34:31,028
I have taken money from
you earlier too.

1645
01:34:31,339 --> 01:34:32,868
I will return it as soon
as I get daddy's draft.

1646
01:34:33,111 --> 01:34:34,108
Don't be silly.

1647
01:34:34,188 --> 01:34:35,948
Is there any difference between
your money and mine?

1648
01:34:36,447 --> 01:34:38,388
I can even give my life for you.

1649
01:34:38,840 --> 01:34:39,948
Now come on.

1650
01:34:40,130 --> 01:34:41,508
Let's go and dance, come on.

1651
01:34:41,588 --> 01:34:42,788
Come on.

1652
01:34:56,707 --> 01:34:58,948
Ramu! Sevak! Gopi!

1653
01:34:59,698 --> 01:35:00,708
Where are you all?

1654
01:35:00,788 --> 01:35:01,602
Yes Vicky sir.

1655
01:35:01,856 --> 01:35:03,348
Who did this to my room?

1656
01:35:03,669 --> 01:35:05,388
I will tell you brother-in-law.

1657
01:35:07,250 --> 01:35:09,468
The happiness that you got seeing
the decoration of this room.

1658
01:35:09,625 --> 01:35:12,024
I should be awarded for it.

1659
01:35:12,308 --> 01:35:13,388
Give me my reward.

1660
01:35:13,468 --> 01:35:16,708
I feel like giving you
such a fitting reward..

1661
01:35:17,338 --> 01:35:19,548
..that you will never dare
to come into my room again.

1662
01:35:20,410 --> 01:35:21,341
Why? Why?

1663
01:35:21,518 --> 01:35:23,108
Have I made a mistake?

1664
01:35:23,238 --> 01:35:25,548
Look, you can do whatever
you want in this room!

1665
01:35:25,948 --> 01:35:27,028
I don't care!

1666
01:35:27,566 --> 01:35:29,388
Just like that, you shouldn't
have any relation..

1667
01:35:29,468 --> 01:35:30,920
..with me and my room!

1668
01:35:31,388 --> 01:35:33,925
If you try to lock horns with
me, then remember this..

1669
01:35:34,209 --> 01:35:35,344
..I am a very bad man.

1670
01:35:35,689 --> 01:35:37,653
You don't have to tell
me that brother-in-law.

1671
01:35:37,781 --> 01:35:38,868
What did you say?

1672
01:35:39,000 --> 01:35:40,188
Vicky!

1673
01:35:40,317 --> 01:35:41,748
Sister-in-law is considered
respectable!

1674
01:35:42,174 --> 01:35:43,188
And you are raising
your hand on her!

1675
01:35:43,476 --> 01:35:46,268
No, no it is not
brother-in-law's fault.

1676
01:35:47,833 --> 01:35:49,188
It is my fault.

1677
01:35:50,830 --> 01:35:52,108
Forgive me brother-in-law.

1678
01:35:53,226 --> 01:35:54,388
Forgive me.

1679
01:35:56,695 --> 01:35:57,748
You should be ashamed.

1680
01:36:00,926 --> 01:36:02,028
Who cares!

1681
01:36:02,353 --> 01:36:03,468
Gopi!

1682
01:36:03,659 --> 01:36:05,788
Ramu! Sevak!

1683
01:36:06,043 --> 01:36:06,948
Why doesn't anyone listen?

1684
01:36:07,028 --> 01:36:09,188
Has everyone gone deaf?
- Madam! Madam! Madam!

1685
01:36:09,268 --> 01:36:11,108
Sevak went to the
market a while ago.

1686
01:36:11,188 --> 01:36:12,716
Where are rest of them?

1687
01:36:12,857 --> 01:36:14,422
Don't they know there is a kitty
party in the house today?

1688
01:36:14,502 --> 01:36:15,548
There is a lot
of work in the house!

1689
01:36:15,773 --> 01:36:18,078
How innocent, you don't
know anything.

1690
01:36:18,224 --> 01:36:18,884
What?

1691
01:36:19,044 --> 01:36:21,628
The servants of this house
have been given leave.

1692
01:36:21,825 --> 01:36:23,948
Leave!
- I mean dismiss.

1693
01:36:24,094 --> 01:36:26,388
I mean, they have been thrown
out of this house.

1694
01:36:26,468 --> 01:36:27,652
Who threw them out?

1695
01:36:28,100 --> 01:36:29,323
Follow me.
- What?

1696
01:36:29,447 --> 01:36:30,468
Sorry, I mean I'll tell you.

1697
01:36:30,906 --> 01:36:32,558
Uneducated! Ignorant! Rude!

1698
01:36:32,638 --> 01:36:33,339
You are telling me!

1699
01:36:33,419 --> 01:36:35,851
No, your daughter-in-law.

1700
01:36:35,931 --> 01:36:37,308
How dare she?

1701
01:36:37,558 --> 01:36:38,948
Hey secretary.

1702
01:36:39,587 --> 01:36:40,628
Here she comes.

1703
01:36:41,028 --> 01:36:42,948
Why do you provoke
her against me?

1704
01:36:43,501 --> 01:36:45,162
I have thrown the useless
servants out of the house..

1705
01:36:45,242 --> 01:36:46,548
..I haven't committed any sin.

1706
01:36:46,783 --> 01:36:48,788
Who are you to give
orders in this house?

1707
01:36:49,306 --> 01:36:51,388
Being the daughter-in-law
of this house..

1708
01:36:51,468 --> 01:36:53,948
..don't I have that much
right, mother-in-law?

1709
01:36:54,526 --> 01:36:57,028
I can see that you are
crossing your limits.

1710
01:36:57,318 --> 01:36:58,548
Is this your father's house?

1711
01:36:58,628 --> 01:37:01,188
Not, but it is my mother-in-law's
house.

1712
01:37:01,469 --> 01:37:03,256
And then I haven't committed
any crime.

1713
01:37:03,468 --> 01:37:05,560
A house where only 4 people live..

1714
01:37:05,707 --> 01:37:07,628
..what's the use of
8 servants there.

1715
01:37:07,748 --> 01:37:09,073
I do half the work.

1716
01:37:09,153 --> 01:37:11,268
Shut up!
- What's that?

1717
01:37:11,348 --> 01:37:12,708
Secretary!
- Yes madam.

1718
01:37:12,788 --> 01:37:13,593
Explain this ignorant woman!

1719
01:37:13,673 --> 01:37:16,308
Calm down! Calm down!
I mean, keep quiet!

1720
01:37:16,388 --> 01:37:17,865
Shut up means keep quiet.

1721
01:37:17,945 --> 01:37:21,388
Say it that way.

1722
01:37:21,468 --> 01:37:22,628
Secretary!
- Madam.

1723
01:37:22,708 --> 01:37:23,788
Follow me!
- Yes, yes.

1724
01:37:25,796 --> 01:37:28,188
There is an interesting story
behind this necklace.

1725
01:37:28,428 --> 01:37:30,499
I had gone to buy something else..

1726
01:37:30,579 --> 01:37:34,388
..in Trikamdas Khimji Zaveri's
shop, I spotted this necklace.

1727
01:37:34,508 --> 01:37:37,108
It is worth 5 lakh rupees.

1728
01:37:37,348 --> 01:37:39,868
This necklace was made
to order by someone.

1729
01:37:39,948 --> 01:37:41,281
Then how did you get it?

1730
01:37:41,361 --> 01:37:42,828
Why wouldn't he give it?

1731
01:37:42,969 --> 01:37:45,348
I told him clearly, if you don't
give me this necklace..

1732
01:37:45,428 --> 01:37:48,748
..the I won't come to your
shop the next time!

1733
01:37:49,036 --> 01:37:50,906
And poor guy, gave it to me.

1734
01:37:51,301 --> 01:37:54,148
And anyway, I am their
regular customer.

1735
01:37:55,131 --> 01:37:56,602
You are really great Kamla.

1736
01:37:56,885 --> 01:38:00,338
Wherever you go, you get your
work done with your influence.

1737
01:38:02,327 --> 01:38:04,765
Leela, why are you sitting
with a sad face?

1738
01:38:05,098 --> 01:38:06,454
I am not in the mood at all.

1739
01:38:06,924 --> 01:38:07,468
Why?

1740
01:38:07,625 --> 01:38:09,068
What shall I tell you?

1741
01:38:09,451 --> 01:38:11,508
When there is a ignorant
daughter-in-law in the house.

1742
01:38:11,831 --> 01:38:14,068
Then how can the mother-in-law
be happy.

1743
01:38:14,316 --> 01:38:16,148
We argue everyday for something.

1744
01:38:16,332 --> 01:38:18,828
Now you tell me, I am the
owner of this house.

1745
01:38:19,191 --> 01:38:20,708
And she gives the orders.

1746
01:38:21,068 --> 01:38:22,828
How can I be in a good mood then?

1747
01:38:23,347 --> 01:38:25,429
Kamla, who is she?

1748
01:38:25,681 --> 01:38:26,828
I never saw her before.

1749
01:38:26,908 --> 01:38:28,566
Her! She is our new maid!

1750
01:38:32,072 --> 01:38:33,748
She is very decked up.

1751
01:38:34,185 --> 01:38:36,596
Mrs. Bhandari, be careful.

1752
01:38:36,828 --> 01:38:39,357
In a house of bachelor boys,
such maids sometimes..

1753
01:38:39,437 --> 01:38:40,828
..play their tricks.

1754
01:38:42,562 --> 01:38:43,687
Why are you sitting here?

1755
01:38:43,767 --> 01:38:46,708
Then should I sit on your lap!

1756
01:38:47,060 --> 01:38:48,308
There was space, so I sat here.

1757
01:38:49,232 --> 01:38:50,028
Will you have grams?

1758
01:38:50,108 --> 01:38:51,308
It is good for your metabolism.

1759
01:38:51,388 --> 01:38:53,548
Seems like she has forgotten
her position.

1760
01:38:54,177 --> 01:38:55,748
I know my position.

1761
01:38:56,260 --> 01:38:57,308
Isn't it mother-in-law?

1762
01:38:57,388 --> 01:38:59,468
Mother-in-law!
- Yes.

1763
01:38:59,585 --> 01:39:01,828
Kamla, what nonsense
is your maid talking?

1764
01:39:01,974 --> 01:39:05,862
Excuse me madam,
don't be deceived!

1765
01:39:06,068 --> 01:39:09,308
I am not the maid, but the
madam of this house!

1766
01:39:09,483 --> 01:39:11,148
I mean, daughter-in-law.

1767
01:39:12,195 --> 01:39:14,708
Mother-in-law, why don't
you tell them?

1768
01:39:14,938 --> 01:39:17,908
Okay, if you don't then
I will tell them.

1769
01:39:18,691 --> 01:39:19,908
Listen carefully.

1770
01:39:20,548 --> 01:39:26,674
I am the wife of his
elder son, Suraj.

1771
01:39:27,698 --> 01:39:31,628
And I know all of you quite nicely.

1772
01:39:32,591 --> 01:39:38,108
All of you come here to brag or
to insult your daughter-in-laws.

1773
01:39:38,459 --> 01:39:41,708
And that's what you teach
my mother-in-law too.

1774
01:39:42,545 --> 01:39:44,286
But listen carefully.

1775
01:39:44,748 --> 01:39:47,428
If that's what you want
to do, then from today..

1776
01:39:47,666 --> 01:39:50,548
..you are not welcome
in this house!

1777
01:39:50,988 --> 01:39:52,228
Did you understand?
You didn't understand!

1778
01:39:52,900 --> 01:39:53,828
This is too much.

1779
01:39:53,908 --> 01:39:56,068
Come on, to hell with
this kitty party.

1780
01:39:56,216 --> 01:39:57,548
We will not come here again.

1781
01:39:57,708 --> 01:39:59,828
Where are you all going?
Please stay.

1782
01:39:59,955 --> 01:40:01,508
Why should we stay?

1783
01:40:01,712 --> 01:40:03,138
Your daughter-in-law
insulted us so much..

1784
01:40:03,320 --> 01:40:06,197
..but you didn't say a word.

1785
01:40:06,379 --> 01:40:07,188
Shame on you!

1786
01:40:07,324 --> 01:40:08,508
Come on!

1787
01:40:08,716 --> 01:40:09,988
Listen.

1788
01:40:10,148 --> 01:40:12,308
Keep listening to your
daughter-in-law.

1789
01:40:17,996 --> 01:40:21,228
Mother-in-law, did I
commit any mistake.

1790
01:40:21,821 --> 01:40:22,948
I only said the truth.

1791
01:40:23,028 --> 01:40:24,108
Stop this nonsense!

1792
01:40:25,095 --> 01:40:29,028
You defamed me in front
of my friends.

1793
01:40:29,505 --> 01:40:32,988
Today I will bring
you under control.

1794
01:40:34,254 --> 01:40:34,988
Mother-in-law!

1795
01:40:35,068 --> 01:40:38,168
I have taught a lesson
to many with this whip!

1796
01:40:38,470 --> 01:40:40,858
If I don't teach you
a lesson today..

1797
01:40:40,938 --> 01:40:42,923
..then my name isn't Kamla!

1798
01:40:46,677 --> 01:40:50,068
Don't think I am a helpless
woman, mother-in-law.

1799
01:40:50,417 --> 01:40:54,628
I am a strong village girl.

1800
01:40:55,425 --> 01:40:58,988
If I make a mistake, then you
can punish me in anyway.

1801
01:40:59,578 --> 01:41:00,828
I won't say anything.

1802
01:41:01,421 --> 01:41:05,308
But if you ever raise your hand
on Shalu without any reason..

1803
01:41:06,641 --> 01:41:08,308
..then be prepared for
the consequences.

1804
01:41:13,378 --> 01:41:14,388
Secretary!

1805
01:41:14,948 --> 01:41:16,308
Save me!

1806
01:41:17,225 --> 01:41:18,628
Fool! Idiot!
- I know!

1807
01:41:19,264 --> 01:41:22,988
She is not weak and delicate
like the city girls.

1808
01:41:23,429 --> 01:41:25,849
She is a solid woman of the village.

1809
01:41:25,929 --> 01:41:27,468
Please excuse me madam.

1810
01:41:27,830 --> 01:41:30,476
If woman would have
been a solid thing..

1811
01:41:30,556 --> 01:41:33,737
..then her name would have been
Dara Singh, Dilawar Khan..

1812
01:41:33,817 --> 01:41:35,188
..Muhammad Ali etcetera.

1813
01:41:35,373 --> 01:41:38,125
Women are delicate.

1814
01:41:38,289 --> 01:41:40,514
She doesn't have any value
in front of a man.

1815
01:41:40,594 --> 01:41:41,844
No, no, except for you.

1816
01:41:41,924 --> 01:41:44,161
Not every woman can be Mrs.
Kamla Bhandari.

1817
01:41:44,241 --> 01:41:45,188
Don't talk nonsense!

1818
01:41:45,366 --> 01:41:48,428
I am getting furious, and you
are blabbering nonsense.

1819
01:41:48,978 --> 01:41:51,548
Think of an idea to defame her..

1820
01:41:52,182 --> 01:41:55,108
..so that the work is done
without much effort.

1821
01:41:55,780 --> 01:41:57,748
I have an action idea.

1822
01:41:58,080 --> 01:42:00,185
With your permission can I say?
- Quickly.

1823
01:42:00,265 --> 01:42:03,228
Look madam, when things cannot
be done the right way..

1824
01:42:03,308 --> 01:42:06,558
..then it's best to
use wrong methods.

1825
01:42:06,868 --> 01:42:09,552
The idea is to shatter her pride.

1826
01:42:10,283 --> 01:42:13,992
Then why don't we hire some
goons and teach her a lesson.

1827
01:42:14,554 --> 01:42:15,588
There you are.

1828
01:42:16,123 --> 01:42:17,428
The idea is not bad.

1829
01:42:18,241 --> 01:42:21,149
But we have to be very careful.

1830
01:42:21,229 --> 01:42:23,788
Don't worry, no one
will know about it.

1831
01:42:24,184 --> 01:42:27,788
Just that, she should go
out of the house alone.

1832
01:42:28,296 --> 01:42:29,228
Alone!

1833
01:42:30,321 --> 01:42:31,868
That can happen only on Tuesday.

1834
01:42:32,564 --> 01:42:35,228
Because she goes to the
temple for veneration.

1835
01:42:35,815 --> 01:42:37,508
Then let Tuesday be the day.

1836
01:42:39,769 --> 01:42:41,748
Come! Come!

1837
01:42:55,610 --> 01:42:58,908
What is it brother, do
you want the offering?

1838
01:42:59,528 --> 01:42:59,913
..Here.

1839
01:42:59,993 --> 01:43:02,572
No dear, we want you
not the offering.

1840
01:43:02,652 --> 01:43:03,708
Wait, wait.

1841
01:43:04,656 --> 01:43:06,822
You want me, isn't it?
- Yes.

1842
01:43:06,902 --> 01:43:08,343
Then I will come along with you.

1843
01:43:08,698 --> 01:43:09,708
Just a minute.

1844
01:44:07,454 --> 01:44:09,156
Hail Lord Krishna!

1845
01:44:55,606 --> 01:44:57,628
Tell me! Who sent you here?

1846
01:44:58,243 --> 01:45:00,228
Tell me, or else I will kill you!

1847
01:45:00,590 --> 01:45:01,388
Tell me!

1848
01:45:01,468 --> 01:45:03,908
I will tell you! I will tell
you! I will tell you!

1849
01:45:04,146 --> 01:45:05,068
I will tell you!

1850
01:45:05,597 --> 01:45:07,748
Thank God you weren't hurt
much sister-in-law.

1851
01:45:09,220 --> 01:45:10,148
Shalu!

1852
01:45:10,300 --> 01:45:11,548
What happened, why have
you tied a bandage?

1853
01:45:11,795 --> 01:45:13,109
Sister-in-law was hurt brother.

1854
01:45:13,341 --> 01:45:16,428
Hurt! Shalu, again you..
- Why are you worried?

1855
01:45:16,981 --> 01:45:19,006
I didn't fight with anyone.

1856
01:45:19,086 --> 01:45:22,046
I had gone to the temple, and there
are monkeys in the temple.

1857
01:45:22,126 --> 01:45:24,589
Seeing the offering in my
hands they came before me.

1858
01:45:24,669 --> 01:45:28,419
While shooing them off,
I slipped and fell!

1859
01:45:28,934 --> 01:45:30,150
Is it paining a lot?

1860
01:45:30,230 --> 01:45:30,988
Shall I call the doctor?

1861
01:45:31,165 --> 01:45:33,496
Doctor! What will the doctor do?

1862
01:45:33,576 --> 01:45:35,751
I have applied clarified
butter and turmeric!

1863
01:45:35,915 --> 01:45:37,798
Even the biggest wounds heal.

1864
01:45:38,715 --> 01:45:41,096
And until I have the grace
of Lord Krishna..

1865
01:45:41,176 --> 01:45:43,708
..and the blessings
of my mother-in-law.

1866
01:45:43,993 --> 01:45:46,489
No one can harm me.

1867
01:45:46,936 --> 01:45:47,947
Isn't it secretary?

1868
01:45:48,027 --> 01:45:51,106
Yes, blessings are very powerful
like electricity.

1869
01:45:51,186 --> 01:45:52,080
Secretary!
- Madam!

1870
01:45:52,160 --> 01:45:54,588
Follow me.
- That way.

1871
01:45:55,544 --> 01:45:57,694
Pinky, how long will we
keep meeting like this?

1872
01:45:58,686 --> 01:46:01,780
I want to get rid of this
distance between us.

1873
01:46:02,498 --> 01:46:03,988
And come along with me to
my home day after tomorrow.

1874
01:46:04,226 --> 01:46:05,357
I will introduce you to my mummy.

1875
01:46:05,574 --> 01:46:06,548
Why is that?

1876
01:46:06,686 --> 01:46:09,788
Until mummy doesn't see how..

1877
01:46:09,868 --> 01:46:13,828
..how can she say yes for
our marriage? - Marriage!

1878
01:46:14,737 --> 01:46:17,639
But Vicky, what's the
haste to get married.

1879
01:46:18,259 --> 01:46:20,828
Right now.. That's fine.

1880
01:46:21,327 --> 01:46:23,117
What's the objection
in meeting mummy?

1881
01:46:23,560 --> 01:46:25,199
She is going to like you.

1882
01:46:25,850 --> 01:46:28,708
That's fine, but I don't have
a proper dress to wear.

1883
01:46:30,689 --> 01:46:32,810
And how can I meet your
mother is these clothes?

1884
01:46:33,297 --> 01:46:34,405
That is no problem.

1885
01:46:34,817 --> 01:46:35,788
You don't have clothes.

1886
01:46:36,754 --> 01:46:38,867
But there are a lot of
clothes in the shops.

1887
01:46:39,914 --> 01:46:42,525
Finish this, after that I
will take you for shopping!

1888
01:46:42,693 --> 01:46:44,545
Buy anything. Okay.
- Okay.

1889
01:46:44,625 --> 01:46:45,788
Let us go. Drink it quickly.

1890
01:46:46,628 --> 01:46:47,723
Flop! Flop! Flop!

1891
01:46:47,882 --> 01:46:51,269
Every idea of your flops
in front of that girl! - I know.

1892
01:46:51,388 --> 01:46:54,779
She is always two steps
ahead of you. - I know.

1893
01:46:54,859 --> 01:46:56,312
She has made my life hell!

1894
01:46:56,392 --> 01:46:57,664
I don't know what to do!

1895
01:46:57,744 --> 01:46:59,911
Sorry madam, even I can't
understand what to do.

1896
01:46:59,991 --> 01:47:01,515
Die of shame!

1897
01:47:01,745 --> 01:47:03,886
You can't think of a good idea.

1898
01:47:04,054 --> 01:47:04,908
That's it.

1899
01:47:05,082 --> 01:47:06,522
I have it madam, I have it.
- What?

1900
01:47:06,602 --> 01:47:09,508
As you said die of shame,
an idea immerged..

1901
01:47:09,588 --> 01:47:11,508
..from the depths of my mind..

1902
01:47:11,588 --> 01:47:14,000
Then say it, you fool!

1903
01:47:14,124 --> 01:47:15,068
Madam, not here.

1904
01:47:15,251 --> 01:47:16,612
Anyone can hear it!

1905
01:47:16,736 --> 01:47:18,132
Follow me.
- Secretary!

1906
01:47:18,212 --> 01:47:19,435
My mistake!
I mean, come here.

1907
01:47:19,515 --> 01:47:20,752
Say that.
- My mistake.

1908
01:47:24,828 --> 01:47:27,308
It is such a beautiful
place, isn't it?

1909
01:47:28,554 --> 01:47:30,348
That's fine,
mother-in-law.

1910
01:47:31,013 --> 01:47:33,596
But I cannot understand one thing.

1911
01:47:34,084 --> 01:47:37,828
Why are you so grateful to me?

1912
01:47:39,083 --> 01:47:41,052
It is not that confusing dear.

1913
01:47:41,553 --> 01:47:43,551
The relation of a mother-in-law
and daughter-in-law..

1914
01:47:43,631 --> 01:47:44,828
..is stronger than the relation
of mother and daughter.

1915
01:47:44,908 --> 01:47:46,471
That's right!

1916
01:47:46,995 --> 01:47:47,908
That's right!

1917
01:47:48,103 --> 01:47:50,398
And there isn't any
mother in the world..

1918
01:47:50,478 --> 01:47:52,005
..who won't be grateful
to her daughter.

1919
01:47:53,526 --> 01:47:58,220
Just wait here for a while, I will
arrange for something to eat.

1920
01:47:58,300 --> 01:47:59,068
Okay.
- Nice.

1921
01:47:59,148 --> 01:48:00,228
Don't go anywhere, stay here.

1922
01:48:11,916 --> 01:48:13,369
Mother-in-law!
- Save me!

1923
01:48:13,449 --> 01:48:14,468
Mother-in-law!

1924
01:48:19,255 --> 01:48:22,676
Doctor sir, what's the
condition of my wife?

1925
01:48:24,293 --> 01:48:26,388
Slowly, why are you
taking the trouble?

1926
01:48:26,745 --> 01:48:29,348
I mean..
- There is nothing to be scared.

1927
01:48:29,607 --> 01:48:30,788
It is a mild attack of pneumonia.

1928
01:48:31,207 --> 01:48:32,028
She will be fine soon.

1929
01:48:32,283 --> 01:48:33,748
She will be fine!
- Sure.

1930
01:48:34,278 --> 01:48:35,228
No, I was just..

1931
01:48:35,705 --> 01:48:37,098
Okay Mr. Bhandari,
I will leave now.

1932
01:48:37,353 --> 01:48:38,308
I will come again in the evening.

1933
01:48:38,471 --> 01:48:39,891
It's fine even if you don't come.

1934
01:48:39,971 --> 01:48:42,618
I mean.. such a big injection
it will pain here.

1935
01:48:43,148 --> 01:48:45,070
But mummy, what was the need
for you to go to the river.

1936
01:48:46,902 --> 01:48:48,410
I was getting bored at home.

1937
01:48:48,490 --> 01:48:49,863
You were getting bored.
- Yes.

1938
01:48:50,199 --> 01:48:52,416
I thought it will be
a nice outing.

1939
01:48:52,817 --> 01:48:54,890
And I will take
daughter-in-law out too.

1940
01:48:55,422 --> 01:48:56,388
Inside the water.

1941
01:48:56,583 --> 01:48:57,708
Tell me one thing.

1942
01:48:58,140 --> 01:48:59,540
How did you fall in the water?

1943
01:49:00,082 --> 01:49:01,146
The water is very scared of you.

1944
01:49:01,226 --> 01:49:03,370
I mean, you are very
scared of water.

1945
01:49:03,774 --> 01:49:07,398
Daddy, someone must have
surely pushed mummy.

1946
01:49:10,131 --> 01:49:13,328
Shall I tell them the truth,
mother-in-law?

1947
01:49:14,374 --> 01:49:16,292
Why are you all so worried?

1948
01:49:16,752 --> 01:49:20,272
I slipped near the shore of the
river and I fell in the water.

1949
01:49:20,796 --> 01:49:22,272
You slipped.
- Yes.

1950
01:49:22,434 --> 01:49:23,512
That means,
along with the tongue..

1951
01:49:23,592 --> 01:49:25,136
..now you can't even control
your feet, isn't it?

1952
01:49:25,216 --> 01:49:27,432
Mr. Bhandari!
- I was just giving an example.

1953
01:49:27,512 --> 01:49:28,872
Every joke has a limit.

1954
01:49:29,587 --> 01:49:30,506
Vicky.

1955
01:49:30,586 --> 01:49:32,192
Why don't you understand
my feelings?

1956
01:49:33,991 --> 01:49:35,032
I love you.

1957
01:49:35,712 --> 01:49:37,632
But even though we stay
under the same roof.

1958
01:49:38,069 --> 01:49:39,352
We are strangers to each other.

1959
01:49:40,192 --> 01:49:41,872
I love you Vicky, I love you.

1960
01:49:42,280 --> 01:49:43,352
Aarti!

1961
01:49:43,984 --> 01:49:45,272
What are you doing in my room?

1962
01:49:47,165 --> 01:49:48,496
Staying in the company
of the ignorant woman..

1963
01:49:48,576 --> 01:49:49,712
..you are becoming ignorant too!

1964
01:49:50,622 --> 01:49:52,272
I ask you, why do you
trouble me always?

1965
01:49:52,778 --> 01:49:54,272
Because I love you.

1966
01:49:54,537 --> 01:49:56,894
But I love someone else.

1967
01:49:57,376 --> 01:49:58,472
I hate you!

1968
01:49:58,783 --> 01:49:59,792
Do you understand?

1969
01:49:59,872 --> 01:50:00,792
I hate you!

1970
01:50:00,872 --> 01:50:02,112
Get out of here.

1971
01:50:03,872 --> 01:50:06,112
Vicky, someone has instigated you.

1972
01:50:06,382 --> 01:50:08,062
Now stop this nonsense, stop it!

1973
01:50:08,318 --> 01:50:11,032
Look Aarti, I will not tolerate
you in my room again.

1974
01:50:11,247 --> 01:50:12,352
Don't come here!

1975
01:50:12,632 --> 01:50:13,952
Why are you still standing here?

1976
01:50:14,032 --> 01:50:14,806
Get out! Get lost!

1977
01:50:14,965 --> 01:50:18,432
I could never have thought, you
will behave like this with me.

1978
01:50:18,591 --> 01:50:21,352
I am going! I will never
bother you again.

1979
01:50:22,032 --> 01:50:23,272
I will not love you too.

1980
01:50:24,032 --> 01:50:25,192
You hate me, don't you?

1981
01:50:25,744 --> 01:50:26,952
I will hate you too!

1982
01:50:27,569 --> 01:50:29,472
Now I won't come back
even if you call me!

1983
01:50:30,068 --> 01:50:31,872
I will never return!
I will never return!

1984
01:50:35,992 --> 01:50:39,512
Aarti, tears are the
symbol of cowardice.

1985
01:50:39,912 --> 01:50:41,072
Yes I am a coward,
sister-in-law.

1986
01:50:41,621 --> 01:50:43,907
I have lost and my heart
has been shattered.

1987
01:50:44,517 --> 01:50:45,912
Yes, I know.

1988
01:50:46,912 --> 01:50:49,257
My brother-in-law has broken
your heart, isn't it? - Yes.

1989
01:50:49,774 --> 01:50:50,832
So what?

1990
01:50:51,361 --> 01:50:54,992
There are sorrows and happiness
on the path of love.

1991
01:50:55,701 --> 01:50:58,370
But Vicky hates me
sister-in-law.

1992
01:50:58,693 --> 01:51:00,752
Some other girl
dwells in his heart.

1993
01:51:02,432 --> 01:51:03,512
Who is she?

1994
01:51:03,752 --> 01:51:04,832
I don't know.

1995
01:51:04,912 --> 01:51:07,752
Whoever she is, she can't
be sweeter than you!

1996
01:51:08,071 --> 01:51:10,974
Because you love
my brother-in-law.

1997
01:51:11,176 --> 01:51:13,166
And love is very strong.

1998
01:51:13,375 --> 01:51:15,672
One day he will surely melt.

1999
01:51:16,018 --> 01:51:18,213
But he is so heartless.

2000
01:51:19,815 --> 01:51:23,832
Foolish, everyone has
feelings in his heart.

2001
01:51:24,413 --> 01:51:25,392
Have patience.

2002
01:51:25,512 --> 01:51:27,352
I will tell you what to do.

2003
01:51:27,536 --> 01:51:29,432
Wipe your tears, and come with me.

2004
01:51:29,972 --> 01:51:32,072
Sanjay, you take everything lightly.

2005
01:51:32,399 --> 01:51:33,392
Why don't you understand?

2006
01:51:33,472 --> 01:51:34,832
The matter is very serious.

2007
01:51:34,912 --> 01:51:36,352
I understand everything, darling.

2008
01:51:36,575 --> 01:51:38,232
Let this act continue
for some more time.

2009
01:51:38,355 --> 01:51:39,912
It is for our own benefit.

2010
01:51:40,352 --> 01:51:41,832
This act cannot continue any longer.

2011
01:51:42,709 --> 01:51:44,992
I fooled Vicky as much as I can.

2012
01:51:45,908 --> 01:51:47,512
He is getting serious day-by-day.

2013
01:51:48,072 --> 01:51:51,280
He is going to take me along with
him to introduce me to his mummy.

2014
01:51:51,933 --> 01:51:53,232
And I cannot do that.

2015
01:51:55,843 --> 01:51:57,442
I love you Sanjay.

2016
01:51:58,054 --> 01:52:01,281
Think of something, how can
we solve this problem?

2017
01:52:01,912 --> 01:52:02,992
He must be arriving.

2018
01:52:03,496 --> 01:52:04,592
Then come on, let
us go to the beach.

2019
01:52:05,007 --> 01:52:06,072
We will think of something there.

2020
01:52:06,377 --> 01:52:07,432
Okay.
- Come on.

2021
01:52:16,346 --> 01:52:17,432
Aarti.

2022
01:52:18,392 --> 01:52:19,512
Follow him!

2023
01:52:19,592 --> 01:52:21,512
And find out who the
wicked woman is..

2024
01:52:21,592 --> 01:52:23,312
..that's creating an obstruction
in the path of your love!

2025
01:52:23,433 --> 01:52:24,912
But sister-in-law.
- No ifs and buts.

2026
01:52:24,992 --> 01:52:26,512
Go quickly. I am telling you.

2027
01:52:32,821 --> 01:52:34,152
Listen Sangita.
- Yes.

2028
01:52:34,335 --> 01:52:35,512
Have you seen Pinky?

2029
01:52:36,012 --> 01:52:37,072
Maybe she has gone
on the beach.

2030
01:52:37,152 --> 01:52:38,232
Which way?
- This way.

2031
01:52:38,344 --> 01:52:39,512
This way!
- Yes

2032
01:52:45,165 --> 01:52:47,432
Darling,
I don't want to meet Vicky.

2033
01:52:48,152 --> 01:52:50,427
This problem should be solved
anyhow, understood.

2034
01:52:50,966 --> 01:52:52,832
Don't worry darling, I will
take care of Vicky.

2035
01:52:53,568 --> 01:52:54,592
Pinky!

2036
01:52:55,578 --> 01:52:56,592
Vicky!

2037
01:53:00,995 --> 01:53:04,127
You cheat! Deceiver!
You betrayed me!

2038
01:53:04,207 --> 01:53:05,512
I will kill you!
- You!

2039
01:53:06,990 --> 01:53:08,232
I won't spare you too!

2040
01:54:23,187 --> 01:54:25,592
Scoundrel! You rascal!

2041
01:54:31,568 --> 01:54:32,543
No!

2042
01:54:32,623 --> 01:54:34,590
Cheat! Betrayer! I
will not spare you!

2043
01:54:34,670 --> 01:54:35,696
Vicky!

2044
01:54:40,199 --> 01:54:41,592
Aarti!
- Vicky!

2045
01:54:41,732 --> 01:54:43,544
Aarti, what did you do?

2046
01:54:43,887 --> 01:54:45,761
Vicky I..
- What did you do Aarti?

2047
01:54:46,072 --> 01:54:48,192
I have answered your hatred, Vicky!

2048
01:54:48,542 --> 01:54:50,992
No Aarti, I will not let you die.

2049
01:55:16,752 --> 01:55:17,992
Doctor sir, how is Aarti?

2050
01:55:18,431 --> 01:55:20,592
We cannot say anything until the
patient doesn't regain conscious.

2051
01:55:21,101 --> 01:55:22,152
We are trying our best.

2052
01:55:22,763 --> 01:55:25,556
Get this injection.
- Okay.

2053
01:55:26,392 --> 01:55:28,472
I will get the injection,
don't worry.

2054
01:55:37,243 --> 01:55:42,392
Lord, till today I haven't
done any good work in life.

2055
01:55:43,093 --> 01:55:45,923
But still I beg of you
for Aarti's life.

2056
01:55:48,101 --> 01:55:49,232
Save her Lord!

2057
01:55:50,593 --> 01:55:51,752
Save her!

2058
01:55:52,448 --> 01:55:53,592
Brother-in-law!

2059
01:55:54,952 --> 01:56:01,592
You are pleading for
that girl's life.

2060
01:56:02,391 --> 01:56:04,552
Don't be a fool, brother-in-law.

2061
01:56:04,632 --> 01:56:06,192
Let that unfortunate girl die!

2062
01:56:06,832 --> 01:56:10,392
She has no one in this
world to cry for her!

2063
01:56:11,339 --> 01:56:15,072
Brother-in-law, you kept
hating her all your life.

2064
01:56:15,764 --> 01:56:17,872
Then why is there sadness
on your face.

2065
01:56:18,023 --> 01:56:20,352
Who are you pleading for,
brother-in-law?

2066
01:56:21,442 --> 01:56:26,217
For her sister-in-law, whose love
I could never understand.

2067
01:56:27,386 --> 01:56:30,032
For saving my life,
she risked her life.

2068
01:56:31,712 --> 01:56:35,392
If something happens to her,
then I will die too.

2069
01:56:35,988 --> 01:56:37,483
I will die too, sister-in-law.

2070
01:56:40,064 --> 01:56:41,032
Don't worry brother-in-law.

2071
01:56:42,119 --> 01:56:43,687
Nothing will happen to Aarti.

2072
01:56:44,828 --> 01:56:47,512
The love for her in your heart.

2073
01:56:48,617 --> 01:56:51,708
It will heal her wounds.

2074
01:56:52,832 --> 01:56:53,872
Yes.

2075
01:56:54,179 --> 01:56:57,352
Sister-in-law, I misunderstood
you too.

2076
01:56:58,789 --> 01:56:59,752
Forgive me sister-in-law.

2077
01:56:59,832 --> 01:57:01,192
What are you doing brother-in-law?

2078
01:57:02,059 --> 01:57:03,703
Humans make mistakes.

2079
01:57:04,269 --> 01:57:05,272
Not Lords.

2080
01:57:06,069 --> 01:57:07,432
Shalu, doctor says
there is no danger..

2081
01:57:07,512 --> 01:57:08,796
..Aarti has regained conscious.

2082
01:57:08,876 --> 01:57:09,872
You go!

2083
01:57:12,431 --> 01:57:13,605
Thank God!

2084
01:57:14,209 --> 01:57:15,832
My brother-in-law has
come to his senses too.

2085
01:57:19,379 --> 01:57:20,604
Wow madam, wow.

2086
01:57:20,778 --> 01:57:21,752
You are great.

2087
01:57:21,872 --> 01:57:25,752
Whenever I see you sitting with
all the family members.

2088
01:57:25,909 --> 01:57:28,512
I think about the great
empress Noorjahan!

2089
01:57:28,672 --> 01:57:32,112
She used to sit like this
in her court. I tell you.

2090
01:57:32,192 --> 01:57:33,352
Secretary sir.
- Yes.

2091
01:57:33,592 --> 01:57:35,832
Where did you see empress
Noorjahan's court?

2092
01:57:35,912 --> 01:57:37,593
You must have seen it in heaven.

2093
01:57:39,050 --> 01:57:40,272
Great!

2094
01:57:40,512 --> 01:57:42,752
Seeing all the members
sitting together

2095
01:57:42,832 --> 01:57:45,512
Talking to each other, it
is such a pleasant sight!

2096
01:57:45,930 --> 01:57:47,592
Here mother-in-law, offering.

2097
01:57:48,378 --> 01:57:49,352
Take it.

2098
01:57:49,432 --> 01:57:51,272
Why are you distributing sweets?

2099
01:57:51,592 --> 01:57:52,672
I had asked for a boon.

2100
01:57:52,817 --> 01:57:53,912
This offering is for that.

2101
01:57:54,432 --> 01:57:55,431
Can I have it?

2102
01:57:55,559 --> 01:57:56,832
Yes, why not.

2103
01:57:57,270 --> 01:58:00,832
You should give the offering
to the beggars first.

2104
01:58:01,232 --> 01:58:03,032
Secretary. Here.

2105
01:58:03,112 --> 01:58:04,511
Thank you.

2106
01:58:04,821 --> 01:58:07,952
At least someone started the
tradition of offerings and boons.

2107
01:58:08,550 --> 01:58:10,832
But dear, what boon
had you asked for?

2108
01:58:11,032 --> 01:58:12,592
For the marriage of
my brother-in-law.

2109
01:58:12,797 --> 01:58:13,832
He has agreed.

2110
01:58:13,912 --> 01:58:16,192
Now we will get him
married very grandly.

2111
01:58:16,272 --> 01:58:17,352
Isn't it brother-in-law..
- What did you say?

2112
01:58:17,972 --> 01:58:20,832
Who are you to decide
my son's marriage?

2113
01:58:21,368 --> 01:58:25,832
I will get him married. To Mr.
Bhanupratap's daughter.

2114
01:58:26,110 --> 01:58:30,592
That will bring a lot.. - She will
bring a flow of money in this house.

2115
01:58:30,853 --> 01:58:32,230
And we will have to change
the name of this house..

2116
01:58:32,310 --> 01:58:33,512
..from Swarg to Gangotri.

2117
01:58:33,812 --> 01:58:36,512
I don't want wealth daddy,
I don't want to be lost in it.

2118
01:58:37,533 --> 01:58:41,552
And that's why I have
decided to marry..

2119
01:58:41,716 --> 01:58:44,672
..an orphan and helpless girl.

2120
01:58:44,924 --> 01:58:45,912
Who is that girl?

2121
01:58:48,408 --> 01:58:49,592
She is standing before you, mummy.

2122
01:58:54,296 --> 01:58:55,919
She! This girl!

2123
01:58:56,352 --> 01:58:58,752
We brought her up, and now..

2124
01:58:58,832 --> 01:59:01,272
..she will be the daughter-in-law
of this house!

2125
01:59:02,512 --> 01:59:04,272
Have you gone mad!

2126
01:59:04,656 --> 01:59:07,512
No mummy, I was mad
but now I am fine.

2127
01:59:08,390 --> 01:59:11,432
And now I have decided,
I will marry only Aarti.

2128
01:59:11,672 --> 01:59:16,272
It's not you, but this ignorant
woman speaking!

2129
01:59:17,031 --> 01:59:19,832
You have learnt to
misbehave from her.

2130
01:59:19,912 --> 01:59:22,432
Mummy, learn to speak properly.

2131
01:59:23,099 --> 01:59:25,112
Sister-in-law is considered
respectable.

2132
01:59:26,650 --> 01:59:29,672
Bravo son, for the first time
you have talked sense.

2133
01:59:30,289 --> 01:59:31,432
Secretary!
- Madam.

2134
01:59:31,512 --> 01:59:32,592
Follow me.
- Definitely.

2135
01:59:37,494 --> 01:59:38,552
Daughter-in-law.

2136
01:59:39,101 --> 01:59:40,232
Give me this offering first.

2137
01:59:40,312 --> 01:59:42,112
I will sweeten my mouth first.
- Here.

2138
01:59:46,555 --> 01:59:53,552
"No body should cast
an evil eye on you.."

2139
01:59:53,992 --> 01:59:56,637
"You are very beautiful.."

2140
01:59:59,331 --> 02:00:01,472
Stop this music!
- Sorry, sorry!

2141
02:00:01,552 --> 02:00:03,002
I was just trying
to divert your mind, madam.

2142
02:00:03,152 --> 02:00:06,472
Tonight is a very painful
night for me!

2143
02:00:06,844 --> 02:00:08,832
I didn't expect this from Vicky,
at least.

2144
02:00:08,912 --> 02:00:09,992
No, no madam.

2145
02:00:10,301 --> 02:00:13,312
If you ask me, then it
is not Vicky's fault.

2146
02:00:13,633 --> 02:00:15,752
He has been instigated against you.

2147
02:00:16,009 --> 02:00:17,383
And it is entirely that
woman's doing..

2148
02:00:17,463 --> 02:00:18,152
- You are right.

2149
02:00:18,336 --> 02:00:22,072
What magic does she have,
that enchants everyone.

2150
02:00:22,275 --> 02:00:23,392
Like P.C Sarkar.

2151
02:00:23,752 --> 02:00:24,872
Great magician.

2152
02:00:25,289 --> 02:00:28,152
One by one,
she has captivated everyone.

2153
02:00:28,302 --> 02:00:29,472
Only Vicky was remaining.

2154
02:00:29,689 --> 02:00:31,352
But today he was captivated too.

2155
02:00:31,432 --> 02:00:32,187
What?

2156
02:00:32,267 --> 02:00:34,992
I mean, he was enchanted
by her too.

2157
02:00:35,330 --> 02:00:37,592
The only thing that's
troubling you..

2158
02:00:37,672 --> 02:00:40,952
..is that simple girl
has made my life hell!

2159
02:00:41,032 --> 02:00:41,992
Get rid of her.

2160
02:00:42,255 --> 02:00:43,152
What do you mean?

2161
02:00:43,232 --> 02:00:44,912
You are misunderstanding me madam.

2162
02:00:45,077 --> 02:00:48,152
I have such a great idea,
that will get rid of her.

2163
02:00:48,278 --> 02:00:49,312
What's that?

2164
02:00:53,195 --> 02:00:53,832
Sorry!

2165
02:00:54,052 --> 02:00:54,992
Secretary.
- Madam!

2166
02:00:55,143 --> 02:00:56,152
Follow me.
- Definitely.

2167
02:00:56,804 --> 02:00:57,832
Wherever you say!

2168
02:00:57,912 --> 02:00:58,992
Wherever you say!

2169
02:00:59,786 --> 02:01:01,232
What are you saying,
mother-in-law?

2170
02:01:01,672 --> 02:01:03,752
Why would I steal?

2171
02:01:04,678 --> 02:01:06,592
Does anyone commit robbery
in their own house?

2172
02:01:06,912 --> 02:01:08,752
Please explain her.

2173
02:01:09,549 --> 02:01:11,335
Yes mother, how that is possible.

2174
02:01:11,752 --> 02:01:12,992
Shalu can never do such a thing.

2175
02:01:13,312 --> 02:01:15,058
I know her very well.

2176
02:01:15,622 --> 02:01:17,771
Why are you talking childishly,
Suraj?

2177
02:01:18,309 --> 02:01:19,367
It doesn't take time for
the milk to get spoiled.

2178
02:01:19,447 --> 02:01:21,072
And the intentions to change!

2179
02:01:21,915 --> 02:01:26,314
This girl had seen
what's in my safe!

2180
02:01:26,552 --> 02:01:28,416
And I am completely sure.

2181
02:01:28,558 --> 02:01:30,072
She has committed the theft.

2182
02:01:30,571 --> 02:01:33,709
And that's why she has come in
this house from the village.

2183
02:01:34,059 --> 02:01:35,472
You can say whatever you
want, mother-in-law.

2184
02:01:35,963 --> 02:01:38,205
But don't accuse me of theft.

2185
02:01:38,392 --> 02:01:41,498
May I die, if I have even
touched your safe!

2186
02:01:41,919 --> 02:01:42,832
Mummy, I saying it again.

2187
02:01:42,912 --> 02:01:43,992
She cannot do such a thing.

2188
02:01:44,312 --> 02:01:46,152
She doesn't have any
greed for anything.

2189
02:01:47,113 --> 02:01:48,759
And still if you are not satisfied..

2190
02:01:48,839 --> 02:01:50,392
..then you can search our room!

2191
02:01:50,672 --> 02:01:52,152
Secretary! Search the place.

2192
02:01:52,536 --> 02:01:53,872
Sevak, search the place!

2193
02:01:58,257 --> 02:01:59,752
Below the watch!

2194
02:02:04,306 --> 02:02:05,392
Behind the statue!

2195
02:02:15,071 --> 02:02:16,912
Below the bed!

2196
02:02:40,410 --> 02:02:41,232
Now tell me!

2197
02:02:41,777 --> 02:02:42,672
Answer me!

2198
02:02:43,161 --> 02:02:44,872
How was this jewellery
found in this room?

2199
02:02:45,669 --> 02:02:48,552
And that too, it was found
in your cupboard.

2200
02:02:49,132 --> 02:02:49,912
No!

2201
02:02:50,070 --> 02:02:53,232
You said, may I die if I
have touched your safe.

2202
02:02:53,703 --> 02:02:55,672
Then, have I kept this
in your cupboard.

2203
02:02:56,069 --> 02:02:58,435
Mother-in-law, I don't know.

2204
02:02:58,825 --> 02:03:01,124
How this came here?

2205
02:03:01,872 --> 02:03:05,192
Dear, you know your
Shalu is not a thief.

2206
02:03:05,382 --> 02:03:06,232
Say something.

2207
02:03:06,450 --> 02:03:07,752
What will he say?

2208
02:03:08,445 --> 02:03:09,472
Secretary!
- Madam.

2209
02:03:09,552 --> 02:03:10,833
Call the police.
- Yes madam.

2210
02:03:10,962 --> 02:03:12,992
Mummy, there is no need
to call the police.

2211
02:03:13,648 --> 02:03:14,632
It will create a scene.

2212
02:03:15,070 --> 02:03:15,872
Fine.

2213
02:03:16,372 --> 02:03:19,249
Ask her to leave this
house right now.

2214
02:03:19,550 --> 02:03:21,518
Sevakram, bring this to my room.

2215
02:03:21,970 --> 02:03:23,392
Secretary. Follow me!

2216
02:03:23,472 --> 02:03:24,552
Yes madam!

2217
02:03:39,182 --> 02:03:42,952
Dear, are you very upset?

2218
02:03:49,765 --> 02:03:53,232
Look, you are dearest to me!

2219
02:03:53,803 --> 02:03:58,232
I swear on you.. I am innocent.

2220
02:03:59,018 --> 02:03:59,912
Yes.

2221
02:04:00,396 --> 02:04:01,872
That's what you say, Shalu.

2222
02:04:03,914 --> 02:04:05,392
But what difference does that make.

2223
02:04:06,807 --> 02:04:10,512
In this house, until my mother
doesn't consider your innocent.

2224
02:04:10,826 --> 02:04:12,992
Neither can I say anything
nor do anything.

2225
02:04:13,712 --> 02:04:17,112
That means.. that means you
feel the same thing.

2226
02:04:17,912 --> 02:04:19,392
That your Shalu is a thief!

2227
02:04:20,239 --> 02:04:23,672
I don't point fingers at anyone
Shalu, I really don't.

2228
02:04:24,728 --> 02:04:26,232
For Gods sake, leave me
alone Shalu, please.

2229
02:04:26,753 --> 02:04:27,832
Mother-in-law.

2230
02:04:30,734 --> 02:04:31,552
You!

2231
02:04:32,995 --> 02:04:35,312
You still haven't left this house!

2232
02:04:36,756 --> 02:04:38,665
What harm have I done
to you, mother-in-law?

2233
02:04:39,166 --> 02:04:43,203
The Lord knows, I didn't
marry your son.

2234
02:04:43,336 --> 02:04:44,998
It was him who made me his wife.

2235
02:04:45,166 --> 02:04:45,992
Not at all!

2236
02:04:46,166 --> 02:04:49,072
A thief can never be our
family's daughter-in-law!

2237
02:04:49,999 --> 02:04:51,472
Don't call me a thief mother-in-law.

2238
02:04:52,064 --> 02:04:53,929
I haven't stolen anything from you.

2239
02:04:54,194 --> 02:04:55,820
You know that very well.

2240
02:04:56,192 --> 02:04:58,992
Why are you ruining my
happily married life?

2241
02:04:59,166 --> 02:05:00,152
Your married life!

2242
02:05:01,155 --> 02:05:04,552
Dreaming about something
more than your status..

2243
02:05:05,091 --> 02:05:07,832
..causes humans downfall.
- No!

2244
02:05:07,912 --> 02:05:09,752
But you didn't think about that!

2245
02:05:10,533 --> 02:05:13,104
That's why, you will
be punished for it.

2246
02:05:13,405 --> 02:05:15,352
There is no place for you
neither in our hearts..

2247
02:05:15,514 --> 02:05:17,832
..nor in our house! Get out of here!

2248
02:05:17,912 --> 02:05:21,124
No! This house is venerable
for me, mother-in-law.

2249
02:05:21,204 --> 02:05:22,152
Get lost.

2250
02:05:22,232 --> 02:05:23,872
Don't call me by that name.

2251
02:05:24,232 --> 02:05:26,105
We don't have any relation!

2252
02:05:26,185 --> 02:05:27,072
Get up.
- No.

2253
02:05:27,152 --> 02:05:29,218
Get out of here!
- I say, get out!

2254
02:05:40,227 --> 02:05:41,072
Thank God!

2255
02:05:42,691 --> 02:05:44,912
Sister-in-law! Sister-in-law!
Sister-in-law!

2256
02:05:45,433 --> 02:05:46,152
Where are you sister-in-law?

2257
02:05:46,372 --> 02:05:47,836
Look, what I have brought for you?

2258
02:05:48,071 --> 02:05:49,046
Vicky.
- Sister-in-law!

2259
02:05:50,043 --> 02:05:50,752
Aarti, where is sister-in-law?

2260
02:05:50,832 --> 02:05:52,458
Aunt threw sister-in-law
out of the house.

2261
02:05:52,538 --> 02:05:53,885
What! Threw her out of the house!

2262
02:05:54,067 --> 02:05:54,832
But why?

2263
02:05:55,047 --> 02:05:56,912
Aunt accused her of thieving.

2264
02:05:57,116 --> 02:05:59,478
And the stolen goods were found
from sister-in-law's cupboard.

2265
02:05:59,616 --> 02:06:00,392
No, that's a lie.

2266
02:06:00,472 --> 02:06:01,672
Sister-in-law can never
do such a thing.

2267
02:06:03,480 --> 02:06:04,912
This is surely someone's conspiracy.

2268
02:06:07,845 --> 02:06:11,351
'Sevak, what are you doing
in brothers room so late.'

2269
02:06:11,431 --> 02:06:12,392
'In brother's room.'

2270
02:06:12,663 --> 02:06:13,552
'I had gone to keep sweet porridge
in brother's room.'

2271
02:06:13,763 --> 02:06:15,872
'Sweet porridge!
- No.'

2272
02:06:17,239 --> 02:06:19,152
'But brother doesn't
eat sweet porridge.'

2273
02:06:19,417 --> 02:06:21,232
'I had gone to keep
in brother's house.'

2274
02:06:22,652 --> 02:06:23,472
'Milk!'

2275
02:06:24,176 --> 02:06:25,385
'Fine go.'

2276
02:06:27,743 --> 02:06:28,392
Vicky!

2277
02:06:28,877 --> 02:06:29,792
Vicky!

2278
02:06:30,007 --> 02:06:30,952
What are you thinking about?

2279
02:06:31,032 --> 02:06:32,232
Nothing, I will just come.

2280
02:06:33,184 --> 02:06:35,251
My name is Chameli..
- Sevak.

2281
02:06:35,331 --> 02:06:39,199
Yes Vicky sir, do you want tea,
coffee, Bournvita or Horlicks.

2282
02:06:39,279 --> 02:06:40,312
I don't want anything.

