2529
02:21:31,062 --> 02:21:32,512
Whatever you said to me,
I listened calmly.

2530
02:21:33,112 --> 02:21:36,352
But I cannot hear a single
world against my father!

2531
02:21:37,421 --> 02:21:40,032
What do you think, I am
ignorant, illiterate.

2532
02:21:40,341 --> 02:21:41,272
Uneducated!

2533
02:21:41,632 --> 02:21:42,752
For your kind information..

2534
02:21:42,832 --> 02:21:44,712
..I am much better educated
than you are!

2535
02:21:45,440 --> 02:21:46,712
I am an Oxford graduate.

2536
02:21:48,341 --> 02:21:52,152
Shalu.. - There is no need
to be shocked Suraj.

2537
02:21:52,734 --> 02:21:55,192
I have evidence of my truth.

2538
02:21:56,933 --> 02:22:00,632
Then.. till today whatever
happened, was that an act?

2539
02:22:00,935 --> 02:22:03,712
Yes, all this was an act.

2540
02:22:04,278 --> 02:22:05,632
And I ended it today.

2541
02:22:06,337 --> 02:22:07,952
Because there is a
limit to tolerance!

2542
02:22:09,924 --> 02:22:13,872
My mother-in-law tried every means
to throw me out of this house.

2543
02:22:14,422 --> 02:22:16,112
She had also made the
plan to get me drunk..

2544
02:22:16,384 --> 02:22:18,952
..and have me insulted
in front of everyone.

2545
02:22:19,330 --> 02:22:21,192
So that you develop
hatred towards me.

2546
02:22:21,650 --> 02:22:24,192
And you throw me out of
this house and your life.

2547
02:22:27,184 --> 02:22:30,112
But mother-in-law, I didn't
drink alcohol today.

2548
02:22:30,996 --> 02:22:34,472
I just swallowed my pride,
and created this scene..

2549
02:22:34,972 --> 02:22:37,272
..so that I get rid
of your ignorance!

2550
02:22:37,947 --> 02:22:41,272
You are very proud of your
wealth and your family.

2551
02:22:41,778 --> 02:22:43,752
I am not from a lowly family too.

2552
02:22:44,843 --> 02:22:48,192
Like you, I am the daughter
of a well-known rich person.

2553
02:22:49,313 --> 02:22:50,992
Do you know who my daddy is?

2554
02:22:53,041 --> 02:22:54,472
Mr. Ashok Mehra!

2555
02:22:58,305 --> 02:23:02,872
Mehra brother, you.. all this..

2556
02:23:03,691 --> 02:23:04,912
Is Shalu your daughter?

2557
02:23:05,829 --> 02:23:07,112
Yes, Mrs. Bhandari.

2558
02:23:08,467 --> 02:23:11,392
I am very proud of my daughter.

2559
02:23:12,535 --> 02:23:15,512
Actually you had seen her
when she was very small.

2560
02:23:16,121 --> 02:23:17,912
Then she went to London
for education.

2561
02:23:18,087 --> 02:23:21,232
But.. but why didn't Shalu
tell us that before?

2562
02:23:21,413 --> 02:23:23,632
Because it was your husband's order.

2563
02:23:26,938 --> 02:23:30,032
This act was put up on his will.

2564
02:23:31,370 --> 02:23:32,952
Daddy and uncle Bhandari wanted me..

2565
02:23:33,548 --> 02:23:36,672
..to come in this house
as Suraj's wife.

2566
02:23:37,613 --> 02:23:39,663
When he kept this problem
in front of me.

2567
02:23:40,013 --> 02:23:42,152
I accepted it as a challenge.

2568
02:23:43,227 --> 02:23:45,912
And I came in this house
by marrying Suraj.

2569
02:23:47,477 --> 02:23:49,536
I tried every way,
mother-in-law.

2570
02:23:50,040 --> 02:23:52,552
But I couldn't make a place for
myself in your heart, mother-in-law.

2571
02:23:53,631 --> 02:23:57,846
God knows, I have a lot
of respect for you.

2572
02:23:58,661 --> 02:24:00,857
Because you are the
mother of my husband.

2573
02:24:01,783 --> 02:24:05,512
I.. lost my mother
in my childhood.

2574
02:24:06,622 --> 02:24:10,293
I thought I will get a
mother's love from you.

2575
02:24:11,284 --> 02:24:13,832
But, I was not destined
for mother's love.

2576
02:24:15,009 --> 02:24:17,072
You didn't even consider me
as your daughter-in-law.

2577
02:24:18,312 --> 02:24:22,152
But today, I want to ask
everyone a question!

2578
02:24:22,941 --> 02:24:25,312
Why is a daughter-in-law
always destined..

2579
02:24:25,392 --> 02:24:26,552
..for her mother-in-law's abuses.

2580
02:24:27,263 --> 02:24:30,312
Is that why she leaves
her parents house..

2581
02:24:30,392 --> 02:24:31,992
..and accepts a strangers family.

2582
02:24:32,394 --> 02:24:34,832
Doesn't she have the right
to any happiness?

2583
02:24:40,806 --> 02:24:41,472
Mother-in-law.

2584
02:24:43,573 --> 02:24:48,712
You can keep your wealth,
your honour and your pride.

2585
02:24:50,589 --> 02:24:51,872
I am leaving.

2586
02:24:53,149 --> 02:24:54,312
Shalu! No!

2587
02:24:54,774 --> 02:24:56,952
As soon as you leave, this house
will turn back into hell.

2588
02:24:57,866 --> 02:25:00,992
And if you still want to leave,
then I will come along too.

2589
02:25:01,072 --> 02:25:05,748
No Suraj, you will find
a wife like me.

2590
02:25:06,511 --> 02:25:07,968
But you won't find a mother.

2591
02:25:08,427 --> 02:25:11,868
No matter how the mother is,
she is respectable.

2592
02:25:12,488 --> 02:25:15,152
Don't leave her for me.

2593
02:25:18,361 --> 02:25:21,123
Shalu.
- Let me go, Suraj.

2594
02:25:21,489 --> 02:25:25,355
If I have committed any mistake,
the please forgive me.

2595
02:25:27,320 --> 02:25:28,152
Come on daddy.

2596
02:25:29,646 --> 02:25:30,472
Wait daughter-in-law.

2597
02:25:31,465 --> 02:25:33,472
Even I want to say
something today.

2598
02:25:34,779 --> 02:25:35,992
For years I kept quiet.

2599
02:25:37,172 --> 02:25:39,312
Even though I knew what is
wrong and what is right.

2600
02:25:39,954 --> 02:25:41,832
I just kept watching
everything silently.

2601
02:25:42,777 --> 02:25:45,992
But today, I have found
my voice again.

2602
02:25:47,371 --> 02:25:49,872
And for the first time
I announce that..

2603
02:25:50,574 --> 02:25:54,953
..neither me or any of my son
will stay in this house.

2604
02:25:57,922 --> 02:25:59,494
What are you saying father-in-law?

2605
02:26:00,269 --> 02:26:01,787
This house belongs to you.

2606
02:26:01,867 --> 02:26:04,832
Dear, firstly this isn't a house.

2607
02:26:05,333 --> 02:26:06,378
It is a prison.

2608
02:26:06,751 --> 02:26:10,392
And this arrogant woman is the
owner of the grand prison.

2609
02:26:11,110 --> 02:26:15,312
And she rules with her stiff
neck, puffed nostrils..

2610
02:26:15,392 --> 02:26:17,152
..and a bitter mouth.

2611
02:26:19,703 --> 02:26:22,472
She gave birth to her sons.

2612
02:26:23,141 --> 02:26:26,152
But she took care of them
like a post dated cheque.

2613
02:26:26,808 --> 02:26:28,312
So that when they are
of marriageable age.

2614
02:26:28,726 --> 02:26:29,992
She can use them.

2615
02:26:31,058 --> 02:26:33,950
She doesn't know.
What sons are?

2616
02:26:34,566 --> 02:26:36,232
What duties a mother
has towards her sons.

2617
02:26:37,002 --> 02:26:38,072
When she doesn't know that!

2618
02:26:38,455 --> 02:26:40,232
How will she know what
is a daughter-in-law!

2619
02:26:40,312 --> 02:26:41,832
What a mother-in-law's duties
are towards her daughter-in-law?

2620
02:26:43,857 --> 02:26:45,152
I had created this scene.

2621
02:26:46,236 --> 02:26:48,632
With the help of my friend.

2622
02:26:49,916 --> 02:26:52,312
So that I can bring my
wife on the right path.

2623
02:26:53,223 --> 02:26:54,232
But I was unsuccessful.

2624
02:26:55,015 --> 02:26:56,682
She didn't come on the right path.

2625
02:26:57,637 --> 02:27:02,771
But I made Shalu's life hell by
bringing her in this house.

2626
02:27:03,691 --> 02:27:04,750
Shalu..

2627
02:27:05,795 --> 02:27:12,007
Just like for Sita, Ayodhya
was wherever Ram dwelled.

2628
02:27:12,623 --> 02:27:15,779
Just like that, our house
will be wherever you live.

2629
02:27:16,741 --> 02:27:18,352
That's heaven for us.

2630
02:27:18,713 --> 02:27:21,432
And after today, this
arrogant woman..

2631
02:27:22,042 --> 02:27:25,192
..will stay in her grand prison
like a wandering soul!

2632
02:27:25,652 --> 02:27:29,574
And will rule her safe, her
jewellery and her furniture.

2633
02:27:29,989 --> 02:27:32,192
And the day she dies,
there won't be anyone..

2634
02:27:32,272 --> 02:27:33,540
..to perform her last rites!

2635
02:27:33,620 --> 02:27:36,192
That day she will remember what
I said and die suffering!

2636
02:27:36,546 --> 02:27:37,112
Come on dear.

2637
02:27:37,466 --> 02:27:39,632
No, no stop!

2638
02:27:40,316 --> 02:27:42,607
Don't punish me so severely!

2639
02:27:43,686 --> 02:27:45,922
I am ashamed of myself.

2640
02:27:46,412 --> 02:27:47,792
Please forgive me!

2641
02:27:48,065 --> 02:27:49,559
Please forgive me!

2642
02:27:49,739 --> 02:27:51,122
Please forgive me!

2643
02:27:51,552 --> 02:27:53,392
I am ashamed of myself.

2644
02:27:55,473 --> 02:27:58,312
Yes Kailash, forgive her.

2645
02:27:59,217 --> 02:28:01,552
She is the mother-in-law
of my daughter.

2646
02:28:02,047 --> 02:28:03,752
And my sister-in-law too.

2647
02:28:05,154 --> 02:28:06,832
Then ask her to apologise to
her daughter-in-law..

2648
02:28:06,912 --> 02:28:08,832
..take her in her arms and say..

2649
02:28:08,912 --> 02:28:11,953
..daughter-in-law's
should be like you.

2650
02:28:12,091 --> 02:28:12,880
Tell her.

2651
02:28:16,616 --> 02:28:18,952
Dear.
- No, what are you doing?

2652
02:28:22,150 --> 02:28:23,512
My child.

2653
02:28:32,343 --> 02:28:33,280
Secretary!

2654
02:28:33,360 --> 02:28:37,226
Secretary where are you going?
- No, no.

2655
02:28:39,150 --> 02:28:40,785
Come on get up, you
are ruining my shoes.

2656
02:28:40,865 --> 02:28:41,832
I was cleaning it.

2657
02:28:42,381 --> 02:28:45,298
So secretary, won't you give your
madam a mischievous idea.

2658
02:28:45,378 --> 02:28:47,192
No sir. Swear on you.
Swear on your father.

2659
02:28:47,272 --> 02:28:48,272
Do you have a father?

2660
02:28:48,499 --> 02:28:50,695
I don't know that sir.
- But your idea, wonderful sir.

2661
02:28:50,775 --> 02:28:52,032
Just wonderful.

2662
02:28:52,112 --> 02:28:53,516
Stop praising, and apologise.

2663
02:28:53,596 --> 02:28:55,237
Yes sir, forgive me.
- Not me, apologise to her.

2664
02:28:55,317 --> 02:28:56,875
To her, yes.

2665
02:28:56,955 --> 02:28:57,721
Forgive me.

2666
02:28:57,801 --> 02:28:58,961
Are you apologising or begging.

2667
02:28:59,041 --> 02:29:01,325
Sorry, sorry, my fault.

2668
02:29:01,405 --> 02:29:02,864
Come on, go there.
- Yes sir, definitely.

2669
02:29:02,944 --> 02:29:05,225
Children..
- Forgive me too.

2670
02:29:06,127 --> 02:29:07,732
So, you have come
on the right track.

2671
02:29:07,997 --> 02:29:08,672
Come children!

2672
02:29:09,287 --> 02:29:10,370
Why are you standing far,
come on.

2673
02:29:10,450 --> 02:29:11,192
Come dear.

2674
02:29:11,900 --> 02:29:13,477
Bless you.

2675
02:29:14,385 --> 02:29:15,857
Mehra.
- Yes Kailash.

2676
02:29:16,012 --> 02:29:17,912
Today even I can say proudly.
- What?

2677
02:29:18,430 --> 02:29:19,992
That wife should be..
- Like her!

2678
02:29:20,072 --> 02:29:22,592
"The rose flower."

2679
02:29:23,307 --> 02:29:31,143
"One in a million is the
face of my beloved."

2680
02:29:31,962 --> 02:29:35,509
"The rose flower."
